<p>Today&rsquo;s episode has John and Dave talking through flaky trackpads, upgrading laptop RAM, the new AirPort Utility, and emptying the trash. They also discuss tricks that might cause your MacBook&rsquo;s trackpad to stop working, how to reconfigure your network with multiple routers, and diagnosing shutdown issues related to Lion&rsquo;s resume functionality. Then, of course, come some tips as well as a fantastic list of Cool Stuff Found. Download today and enjoy!</p>
